**Asked:** Verify panel body scrollbar matches spec (thin, custom styled).  
**Did:** Found existing scrollbar CSS in `Overlay.tsx`, fixed width from 5→6px, replaced 3 hardcoded rgba values with `theme.ts` token references (`surface.track`, `blackAlpha(0.2)`). No new errors introduced.
